  "instructions": [
    "Heat oil in a large Dutch oven over medium-high heat.",
    "Add the pork and cook until browned on all sides, about 5 minutes.",
    "Add the onion, ginger, and garlic and cook until the onion is translucent.",
    "Add the star anise, mustard powder, fish sauce, and sugar and cook for 1 minute.",
    "Add the potatoes, beef broth, and water and bring to a boil.",
    "Cover the pot and transfer to the oven.",
    "Braise for 2 1/2 hours, or until the meat is tender and the potatoes are cooked through.",
    "Stir in the bean sprouts and cook for an additional 10 minutes.",
    "Serve hot, wrapped in a ssam wrap or with steamed rice."
